Package com.hdmstuttgart.fluffybear.model

Class Recipe

java.lang.Object
com.hdmstuttgart.fluffybear.model.Recipe
@Entity
public class Recipe
extends java.lang.Object
Class for modelling an recipe by uid, name, image, cooking time, category (breakfast, lunch, dinner) wether it is vegetarian/vegan, needed ingredients and cooking instructions.

    • addIngredient

      public void addIngredient​(Ingredient ingredient)
      Instanciates new RecipeIngredient with given Ingredient instance beeing assigned to the ingredient member variable and the self reference to the recipe member variable. The RecipeIngredient instance is beeing added to the ingredients list.
      Parameters:
      ingredient - ingredient instance to be added to the new RecipeIngredient instance.

    • removeIngredient

      public void removeIngredient​(Ingredient ingredient)
      Iterates over all RecipeIngredient instances and removes every the each instance with matching Ingredient instance referenced by the ingredient member variable.
      Parameters:
      ingredient - ingredient instance that defines which RecipeIngredient instance is going to be removed.
